&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Technical Delivery and Deployment&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build end-to-end POCs and MVPs alongside customer engineering teams, working inside their codebases, infrastructure, and constraints.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;For customers whose core product is built on GenAI, architect the inference foundations

