&lt;li&gt;Develop pre-event, day-of, and post-event engagement strategies that maximize registration-to-attendance conversion and sales follow-up&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work hand-in-hand with sales teams to build targeted invite lists and ensure strong attendance from priority accounts&lt;/li&gt;
