&lt;li&gt;Are a strong cross-functional collaborator who can work effectively with Sales, Partnerships, Creative, Communications, and executive stakeholders&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working cross functionally with sales leadership, sales representatives, customer success, creative, content, and product marketing.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficient in CRM and marketing automation software, must is Salesforce&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
