&lt;p&gt;The Head of Marketing Operations builds the infrastructure that lets Fireworks marketing scale, and runs the operating system that keeps the team performing day to day. You own the marketing tech stack, the data model, the lifecycle, and the analytics that turn marketing into a predictable pipeline engine that the executive team can trust. You also own the planning rhythms, budget, prioritization, and program management that keep every function inside marketing shipping on time and in sync.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The right person is rigorous, opinionated about tooling, and energized by the operational problems most marketers avoid. You think about marketing the way a great operator thinks about a business: cadence, accountability, resource allocation, and clear measurement.&lt;/p&gt;
