&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location and Work Style&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role is remote-friendly within the US. You will travel to our San Mateo HQ periodically for team onsites, planning sessions, and key moments that benefit from being in person. We will establish a cadence that works for the team and the role.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
