&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Reproduce and Extend State-of-the-Art:&lt;/strong&gt; Implement and reproduce results from recent machine learning papers. Identify bottlenecks, propose improvements, and scale these methods to larger datasets and models.&lt;/li&gt;
