&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bridge Science and Engineering:&lt;/strong&gt; Translate abstract mathematical concepts and research ideas into robust, bug-free, and efficient code.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Collaborate Cross-Functionally:&lt;/strong&gt; Work closely with Research Scientists to unblock their experiments by providing tooling, optimizing code, and co-designing experiments that are hardware-aware.&lt;/li&gt;
